data.description: Beautiful yet spacious home with large family room, separate dining room with hardwood floors. Come relax on the screened in porch near the lake. Master on main with extra seating area, master en-suite with separate walk-in shower and garden tub. Relaxing sun room or office space with separate entry. Upstairs features two additional large bedrooms, which leads to bonus rooms on each side of each bedroom. Two bonus rooms would make great additional bedrooms, movie room, or additional storage space. Over a half an acre lot located in a cul-de-sac, nice size fence, backyard, walking distance to lake with access. Call now for showing!
